cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CE 

The paper proposes an approach based on matrix factorization for energy disaggregation, which is a problem related to signal processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Signal Processing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
